Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.83,0:00:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,侵入秋葉原集群的偷渡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.92,0:00:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,與巡視員交火後目前仍然在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.86,0:00:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,萬世橋為慶祝發放烤肉便當 領取的群眾排隊成長龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,偷渡屋的破壞引發的森林火災依然持續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.32,0:00:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,受災的低保群眾發動遊行要求改善待遇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,還有多數博物館遭劫掠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,任關八州聯合會長的黑道頭目 侃王八百八氏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.28,0:00:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,發表了批評偷渡屋的言論
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,他說他們是唆使模範黑道違背俠義之道的異端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,據奮戰中的無人機巡視員同志報告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.27,0:00:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,卑劣的偷渡屋依然在逃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.99,0:00:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因偷渡屋的暴亂 東部商廈破環嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,因偷渡屋的槍擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因偷渡屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.27,0:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易到了三軒茶屋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,店全都關了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,明明有好多美食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.53,0:03:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,戒嚴令就是因為我們發的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.33,0:03:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,話說 目標的端末呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.61,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.70,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是傳說中的端末
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,對 是公共電話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然聽說過 沒想到在這個地方藏著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,現在多數線路已被切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想聯絡M只能靠這部電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.06,0:03:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是最後的希望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,龜速線路
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微費點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.66,0:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,趁現在休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.29,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,連線結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.14,0:04:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,收到了M的回信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,內容呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,只有文本和垃圾文件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.55,0:04:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,蜥蜴斷尾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,玩完了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.66,0:04:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這回復好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,接受現實吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.21,0:04:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,就算拋棄我們 M的措辭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也不會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,讓我看看附件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,無意義的音訊檔案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,就算聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,播放吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,單純的雜音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.74,0:05:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有嵌入代碼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.04,0:05:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,此處不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,但是好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我了解你的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.74,0:05:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.24,0:05:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.28,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這個節奏是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是舞曲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿呦呦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿呦呦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.10,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,聽 聽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,這節奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.12,0:05:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是開溜舞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,M說 他想逃離
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個世界的管理者嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.08,0:06:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,對 不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.17,0:06:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼那麼肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.05,0:06:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,因為這舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,是我想出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,這是和M定好的暗號
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.68,0:06:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能會錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你不會真打算幫他逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,先撤離吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,走後門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.77,0:07:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.88,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣下去要筋疲力盡了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,沒子彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,現在只能逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,加把勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.72,0:08:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.40,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不能丟下你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.88,0:08:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,想在這同歸於盡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不見 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.23,0:08:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.89,0:08:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,世上無論何事都需要覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,偷渡屋 黑道 魔法少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.09,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,堅持不可讓步的原則
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.24,0:09:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,阿卡姆 阿卡姆 蒂林哈斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.95,0:09:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,獨白朗讀匯於一發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一發乾掉那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.19,0:09:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,一發 一發
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,一發？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.04,0:09:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,一髮屋 十一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.96,0:09:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,魔法少女十一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,前來華麗助戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.98,0:10:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡暫時是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓菲利斯好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 十一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 你真是那個頭頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,當然了 馬爾提
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小姑娘 要懂得點到為止
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,三軒茶屋的仲裁者也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道是藏不下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.55,Top,,0,0,0,,給我個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.52,0:10:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我能幫你的只有食物和彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.28,0:10:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,還有稍微帶帶路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,之後怎麼打算的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.75,Top,,0,0,0,,什麼東西 真難喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你就告訴我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,因為有人告訴我想要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.95,0:11:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不得不逃的是艾庫亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,身為黑道說想成為魔法少女時
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞也沒有嘲笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,還說支持我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,回想起來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,因為偷渡屋的一句話我便得到了救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.66,0:11:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,十一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,只是突然想說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞的心情是真心實意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.22,0:12:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.25,0:12:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,逃出路線定好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,走西門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要去東門
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.54,0:12:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,學姐 那不是市中的方向嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.16,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那邊就是大橋集群了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.68,0:12:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全是病人的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.96,0:12:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,處理傷口就不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,途徑大橋集群
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.77,0:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,再經過澀谷和青山
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,目的地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,是大江戶城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.66,0:12:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大江戶城
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,說真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.20,0:12:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是管理員坐鎮的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,M正向我們求助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不能坐視不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是聽說大江戶城是警備最森嚴的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,即使如此 也不能放棄委託人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.84,0:13:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.92,0:13:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看清形勢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才都那麼狼狽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,就這還想衝進大江戶城
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是去自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒打算自殺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了絕地之幸還能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,被流彈擊中就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,這
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我沒有自信能保護好你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.02,0:13:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,恕不奉陪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.57,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣去很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.38,0:14:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這與赤膊上陣無異
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 不會連累菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的只有這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,承蒙照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.36,0:14:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.47,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣真的不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.90,0:14:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有什麼不滿就快點說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是對你不滿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.46,0:14:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是阿汪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞學姐 我看不慣這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼沒挽留菲利斯學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,這算什麼 這樣太糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.10,0:15:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然她不在了我就能獨占艾庫亞學姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.44,0:15:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和馬爾提一樣喜歡學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然而這是什麼態度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.72,0:15:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就那麼從容嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我也不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我終於找到了一個學姐的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.15,0:15:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,無論說什麼都不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.84,0:15:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.73,0:15:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,對對方完全沒興趣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.14,0:15:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.39,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,對對方不抱任何期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,所以不會生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,對我也是 對她也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.59,0:16:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如果馬爾提說要退出的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.42,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就像剛才那樣表示理解然後辭別嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那我該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.09,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.67,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,跟我來 為了我跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你對我是必要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你的幫助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我只能依靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.99,0:16:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她剛才肯定在等這句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,然而艾庫亞學姐哪怕說了一句嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 要是馬爾提的話肯定會跪地嚎啕大哭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,硬撐著的菲利斯學姐肯定很失落
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提的不滿就這些
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,馬爾提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好結束 這個話題到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要放棄攻城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.62,0:17:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.64,0:17:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是破天荒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,多嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.92,0:18:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,艾庫亞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.70,0:18:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.21,0:18:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.67,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事 話說你輕點
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 菲利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 請跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我還是需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:19:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 剛才怎麼沒挽留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.07,0:19:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,走神了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.69,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因為擔心你的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但我還是不願這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.06,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很危險 但是請跟我走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,幫幫我吧 協助我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我絕對需要你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.58,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.11,0:19:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我很困擾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,困擾也要來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.62,0:19:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.63,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,最初就該這麼強硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.98,0:19:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 這多虧了馬爾提斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.37,0:19:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 回到大家那裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.82,0:19:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我說 那個史萊姆怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我好在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,說明一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,您先請
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.54,0:20:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.03,0:20:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,總之潛入進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.97,0:20:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不歸隊也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,還是要謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 還差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,直到最後請各位多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒問題 艾庫亞學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.18,0:21:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,不至於 抬起頭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.37,0:21:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,開衝吧 領導
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.38,0:21:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,請稍等 M
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對幫你逃走
